      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * Discord Channels</b>\n</p><p>Computer chess is actively discussed in several Discord channels:\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://discord.com/invite/GWDRS3kU6R\">Stockfish Discord</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://discord.com/invite/pKujYxD\">Leela Chess Zero Discord</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://discord.com/invite/F6W6mMsTGN\">Engine Programming Discord</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://discord.com/invite/9MVg7fBTpM\">OpenBench Discord</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://discord.gg/kWDrFSB2GG\">Unofficial CPW Discord</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://discord.gg/lichess\">Lichess</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://discord.com/invite/3VbUQME\">chess.com</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Discord_Channels&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: See also\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Computer Chess Forums</a>\n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Discord_Channels&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2020_...\">2020 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Discord_Channels&amp;